  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6df658ea-8887-42a6-b6a0-8353be0713ac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a1a28a37-6fa6-4903-aed9-120ee58867dd\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-474beb28-1d86-43a1-a90e-c9b1703ea383\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 30</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-316481cf-ee71-48b7-b06b-1059a4ffd750\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-597c9f10-ccfd-4988-bdbb-b43f7852913e\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-46ebe467-14a9-43e2-b0c7-d1f1bf027c96\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b558449c-5611-4195-94ed-e4419fbbcaef\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[본격적인 스토리보딩 작업]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bdc86580-64ec-482a-9684-63e24afdfb67\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-a5709560-14ef-4b43-bd0b-75b38a3feeed\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>이제 본격적으로 스토리보딩 작업에 들어갑니다. 지금까지는 자료나 개념에 대해 심도있게 생각했습니다. 물론 아직은 미흡한 부분이나 보강해야하는 사항이 있지만 앞으로 채워나가도록 하겠습니다. 이제부터는 하나하나 PPT 파일을 정리하도록 하겠습니다. 이제 시작입니다. 약 두달 뒤 나름 완벽한 (주)파파스컴퍼니 기획문서가 완성되기를 희망해 봅니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87dafdef-fda6-4225-a9e5-47ae74c2cd5d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-default\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-47f3dab1-34b6-47af-9d66-2f8d3d3ca6c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0fdb104a-dfc2-45cf-8dca-4fa9f5dee7a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>희망은 좋은거죠. 가장 소중한 것이죠. 좋은것은 절대 사라지지 않아요.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-471effa4-9708-4ab0-9356-34e5f18570bb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-02cc74be-fa69-4266-9d57-d6e60287d94f\" style=\"\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da3a981f-3038-400e-b68c-773014adca2d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-19c7f4ad-86eb-4dce-8d5c-78d1eff9e16c\" style=\"\">앤디 듀프레인</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8f742eb4-9225-4730-9195-ed49432c2a72\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4a8050da-82f7-4309-9490-d1840ee3f8ab\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-256da02f-9b81-4fc6-8fc3-4f06057a9ed1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-54ac836a-38a3-41a4-bc16-159405735de1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:709px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link